<H3> <TI>   Police, Army Maltreat `Dozens' of Ethnic Albanians </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1602180294 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1735 
GMT 16 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1602180294 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana TVSH Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Albanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Reports from Prishtina confirm that recently the 
Serbian police and army have maltreated dozens of Albanian 
citizens who live in Morine near the Kosova-Albanian border area. 
  The Serbian police repression has also been continuing in 
many villages in Podujeve. In Dyze in this commune, 17 Albanian 
homes have been raided. 

</TEXT>

