  [Text] Warsaw, Feb. 15 -- Defence Minister Piotr 
Kolodziejczyk called WASHINGTON POST's report that Poland had 
sold arms to U.S. in the 1980s a provocation. 
  Commenting on the WASHINGTON POST's article in the TV 
evening news bulletin "Panorama" on Tuesday, Kolodziejczyk said: 
