<H3> <TI>   Academics Refuse To Relinquish Academy to Serbs </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1602095894 Tirana ATA in English 0919 GMT 16 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU1602095894 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pristine, February 16 (ATA) -- Representatives of 
the Serbian authorities located forcibly in Kosova went again to 
the Academy of Sciences and Arts of Kosova with new threats and 
demanded to the Albanian academics to give the Academy building 
up and to handle the keys. The Academy's refusal was 
determined. Based on the decisions of the Extraordinary Serbian 
Assembly, the Serbian authority takes the Kosova Academy 
building and its property. 
  Many personalities of the state, politics, and science who 
have protested against the Serbian warnings to abolishing the 
Kosova Academy, are expecting the international support for 
protecting the highest Albanian science institution in Kosova. 

</TEXT>

