<F P=104>  Budapest Kossuth Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hungarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Border Guard action units are on permanent alert 
along the southern border in case of possible NATO air strikes 
in Bosnia, Border Guard Spokesman Attila Krisan said. He added 
that at the moment there are no signs of border provocations. 
