Russian initiative the Serb side today began withdrawal its 
heavy artillery around Sarajevo. A column of 30 pieces of heavy 
artillery started being withdrawn from Lukavica at 1300 [1200 
GMT], a TANJUG correspondent in Lukavica reports. 
  "By order of the Supreme Command, the artillery pieces were 
