  [Excerpt] Edit Schranz is on the line from the national 
convention of the Hungarian Democratic Forum [MDF] where a press 
briefing is being held by the newly elected chairman. 
  [Schranz] The seventh national convention of the MDF has 
elected Lajos Fur as party chairman. Out of the 729 votes cast, 
685 were in favor and 44 votes were invalid. [passage omitted] 

