<H3> <TI>   World Bank Grants $80 Million Loan </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1902120894 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
in Slovak 1100 GMT 19 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1902120894 </F>
<F P=104>  Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
in Slovak 1100 GMT 19 Feb 94 </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Slovak </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An agreement on an $80-million loan to the Slovak 
Republic has been signed at the World Bank in Washington. The 
loan is earmarked for economic recovery and will be used to 
boost foreign currency reserves. The terms of the loan are 
advantageous, and its repayment will begin in August 1999. 

</TEXT>

